content: Data development engineer
数据开发工程师

This role has operational permissions for all features in the data enablement module, permissions for model services in the model enablement module, and permissions for service access in the settings.
该角色拥有数据使能模块所有功能的操作权限，拥有模型使能模块模型服务的操作权限，拥有设置中服务接入的操作权限。
Full-stack development engineer
全栈开发工程师
This role has full operational permissions for the data enablement module, model enablement module, and application enablement module, as well as permissions to manage service access in the settings.
该角色拥有数据使能模块，模型使能模块，应用使能模块的全部操作权限，拥有设置中服务接入的操作权限。
Application development engineer
应用开发工程师

This role has operational permissions for dataset management and the knowledge base in the data enablement module, operational permissions for model services in the model enablement module, full operational permissions in the application enablement module, and operational permissions for service access in the settings.
该角色拥有数据使能模块数据集管理和知识库的操作权限，拥有模型使能模块模型服务的操作权限，拥有应用使能的全部操作权限，拥有设置中服务接入的操作权限。
Application visitor
应用访问人员
As a visitor, this role only has permission to use the applications that have been published in the application market within the application enablement module.
该角色作为访问者，只拥有使用应用使能模块中应用市场已发布了过的应用的权限。
Model development engineer
模型开发工程师
This role has operational permissions for dataset management in the data enablement module and full operational permissions for all functions in the model enablement module.
该角色拥有数据使能模块数据集管理的操作权限，拥有模型使能模块所有功能的操作权限。
Data application development engineer
数据应用开发工程师
This role has all operation permissions on the data enablement module and application enablement module, and has the read-only permission on the model enablement module.
该角色拥有数据使能模块以及应用使能模块的全部操作权限，拥有模型使能模块只读权限。
Application development trial engineer
应用开发体验工程师
This role has the operation permission on the application enablement module and the read-only permission on the data enablement module and model enablement module.
该角色拥有应用使能模块的操作权限，拥有数据使能与模型使能模块的只读权限。
